  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69ad9c7c92d6036da63256cf",
      "text": "話しかけやすい服",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1772985484,
      "updated": 1772985485
    },
    {
      "id": "69ad9c8e0000000000e512e7",
      "text": "という[ベルメソン]の[広告]",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1772985486,
      "updated": 1772985631
    },
    {
      "id": "69ad9c990000000000e512e9",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/5f539fb8a02ebf5e1dcab70c1135ea8c]",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1772985498,
      "updated": 1772985498
    },
    {
      "id": "69ad9c9a0000000000e512ea",
      "text": "どちらで解釈したか？",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1772985498,
      "updated": 1772985527
    },
    {
      "id": "69ad9cb60000000000e512eb",
      "text": "A. この服を着ると同僚に話しかけやすい！第一印象UP！",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1772985527,
      "updated": 1772985550
    },
    {
      "id": "69ad9cb60000000000e512ec",
      "text": "B. この服を着ると同僚から話しかけられやすい！第一印象UP！[terang.icon][はるひ.icon]",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1772985527,
      "updated": 1772987147
    },
    {
      "id": "69ada2d80000000000abc20c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1772987096,
      "updated": 1772987102
    },
    {
      "id": "69ada2df0000000000abc20d",
      "text": " ぱっと見で「服に話しかける」だった汗[はるひ.icon]",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1772987104,
      "updated": 1772987172
    },
    {
      "id": "69ada2f70000000000abc20e",
      "text": "  マスコット付き的な…",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1772987127,
      "updated": 1772987174
    },
    {
      "id": "69ad9cb60000000000e512ed",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1772985527,
      "updated": 1772985527
    },
    {
      "id": "69ad9cc30000000000e512ee",
      "text": "広告の本文を見ると正解はわかる",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1772985540,
      "updated": 1772985564
    },
    {
      "id": "69ad9ce90000000000e512ef",
      "text": "\t正解、というか広告主の意向",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1772985577,
      "updated": 1772985583
    },
